  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>These high-quality self-catering ski-in/ski-out apartments are conveniently located just opposite the main hotel building where optional pre-bookable half board meals can be taken. All suites enjoy free use of the main hotel facilities, have their own en suite sauna and are beautifully furnished and equipped to a high standard. They offer an attractively priced upgrade to the standard hotel room accommodation. All suites enjoy a scenic elevated position 100m from the Pyhätunturi Hotel, amin ski slopes, ski school and ski hire shop. A good supermarket is located 900m away in the village centre.</span></p>]]></description>
